# NMLabs Stdlib C

## Introduction
This is a library for C projects by Nextreamlabs. It is used to complement the C stdlib where some functions/facilities are missing.

## Authors and Contributors
* [Alessandro Molari](http://molarialessandro.info)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
name: Nmlabs-stdlib-c
tagline: The C library that puts a little bit of sugar in the coffee
